Simple Trend is an easy-to-use utility that scans and stores network information. It allows you to easily discover and alert on changes on a network over time. 

Features: 
 * Automated Internal/External Scans
 * Flexible Querying/Alerting System
 * Parsing Nmap XML results
 * Easy access to Nmap's data in a database ( SQLite, MySQL or Postgres)
 * Runs on Linux, BSD and Windows

Similar Projects:
 * PBNJ - http://pbnj.sourceforge.net/
 * Nmap - http://insecure.org

